    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Transliteration Tool\\n\",\"**NLP Project 65 of 100** — Convert names/text between scripts (Latin ↔ Devanagari, Cyrillic, etc.).\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import re\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Simple Latin → Devanagari transliteration mapping\\nLATIN_TO_DEVANAGARI = {'a':'अ','aa':'आ','i':'इ','ee':'ई','u':'उ','oo':'ऊ',\\n    'ka':'क','kha':'ख','ga':'ग','cha':'च','ja':'ज','ta':'त','tha':'थ',\\n    'da':'द','dha':'ध','na':'न','pa':'प','pha':'फ','ba':'ब','bha':'भ',\\n    'ma':'म','ya':'य','ra':'र','la':'ल','va':'व','sa':'स','ha':'ह'}\\n\\n# Latin → Cyrillic (Russian approximation)\\nLATIN_TO_CYRILLIC = {'a':'а','b':'б','v':'в','g':'г','d':'д','ye':'е',\\n    'zh':'ж','z':'з','i':'и','k':'к','l':'л','m':'м','n':'н','o':'о',\\n    'p':'п','r':'р','s':'с','t':'т','u':'у','f':'ф','kh':'х','ts':'ц'}\\n\\ndef transliterate(text, mapping):\\n    result = []\\n    i = 0\\n    text_lower = text.lower()\\n    while i < len(text_lower):\\n        matched = False\\n        for length in [3, 2, 1]:\\n            chunk = text_lower[i:i+length]\\n            if chunk in mapping:\\n                result.append(mapping[chunk])\\n                i += length\\n                matched = True\\n                break\\n        if not matched:\\n            result.append(text_lower[i])\\n            i += 1\\n    return ''.join(result)\\n\\n# Test\\nfor name in ['namaste', 'karma', 'yoga', 'guru', 'dharma']:\\n    dev = transliterate(name, LATIN_TO_DEVANAGARI)\\n    print(f'{name:12s} → Devanagari: {dev}')\\n\\nprint()\\nfor name in ['ivan', 'nikita', 'boris', 'sasha']:\\n    cyr = transliterate(name, LATIN_TO_CYRILLIC)\\n    print(f'{name:12s} → Cyrillic: {cyr}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Rule-based transliteration uses character mappings** between scripts.\\n\",\"- **Covers basic Latin → Devanagari/Cyrillic** conversion.\\n\",\"- **For production, use libraries like `transliterate` or `indic-transliteration`.**\\n\",\"- **ML-based transliteration handles ambiguous mappings** better.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
